Time for a huge update!! Introducing Insights a new design 2 new quick entry types Mood Gratitude additional notifications and custom emotions! Insights: Use personalized insights to discover more about yourself such as which cognitive distortions do you make the most Or how does your mood vary depending on day and time Design: Now your entries are easier to access than ever before without needing to purposely View Entries Quick Entry Types: We heard you loved Check Thoughts as an easy shortcut to do a specific part of the full entry so we added two more quick entry types! Now you can record your mood in just 2 taps and quickly write down something you re grateful for. Extra Notifications: Pro Users can now schedule additional notifications in the morning afternoon evening and nighttime. Custom Emotions: Pro users can now customize an unlimited number of positive and negative emotions.
